All Go tests pass. Fixed the following migration issues:

**migrations/000022_create_print_quotas.up.sql:**
- Quoted reserved keyword `limit` as `"limit"` (column definition and function reference)

**migrations/000024_create_secure_release.up.sql:**
- Removed foreign key `REFERENCES printers(id)` from array column `assigned_printers UUID[]` (PostgreSQL doesn't support FKs on arrays)

**migrations/000026_create_analytics.up.sql:**
- Moved `COALESCE`-based UNIQUE constraints to separate unique indexes (can't use functions in inline UNIQUE constraints)
- Quoted reserved keywords `date` and `month` as `"date"`, `"month"`
